      "description": "This is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L powerplant equipped with individual throttle bodies and precision-tuned double-VANOS. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual and a M-Variable differential lock, ensuring optimal power delivery. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring a factory-straight subframe and pristine suspension bushings. Every mechanical component, from the valve clearances to the cooling system, has been maintained to an exacting standard. Finished in original paint with an untouched interior, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering.",
