      "description": "Available now is a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with no creasing or bolster wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All electronics, displays, and safety features function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time using only OEM parts. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather use. Included are all original keys, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, and a folder of service receipts. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle.",
